"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"To expand the scope of ideas & spur creative thinking, we’re introducing specific idea bounties to the [World’s Fair: Stories of The Future](https://mirror.xyz/0xd340d824F8A2BC6C7172b63B675B97E72eDD14F7/27hy4ChBZ-uX0_F9CdNvuyzNu2bRFFvWqj0ynm_dwjI) short story contest.\\n\\n### Share an Idea\\n\\nIf you're a builder, researcher, inventor, or simply a believer in the future we invite you to contribute specific bounties to the competition. These bounties will serve as free or paid rewards for stories that feature certain concepts, grapple with certain questions, or explore different topics that writers can incorporate into their stories.\\n\\nUpon submission, we'll review the bounty for clarity and then add it to the public directory. Once submissions close on February 15, 2022 we'll contact you with the essays from writers who completed your bounty to help judge.\\n\\n**Submit here:**  <https://airtable.com/shrTf8BW2lWdVj2hW>\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Find an Idea\\n\\nWe've intentionally left this prompt vague — we want you to imagine a future you’re excited about. That said, if you could use some additional constraints, we've sourced topics and added additional bounties on concepts you can incorporate into your story!\\n\\nEach bounty will be judged separately and these prizes exist on top of the World's Fair Co prize pool. If selected as a bounty award, the story follows the same rights retainment.\\n\\nPlease make sure to include any bounties you're writing about in your submission form.\\n\\n**View Open Bounties here:** <https://airtable.com/shrsiXz5cjCQ7xI5s/tblMbX5gVpQOp7hot>\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Questions?\\n\\nIf you have questions about completing a bounty, submitting a bounty, or something else (we love random emails too!) please contact us at: stories@worldsfair.co. \\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n*Cover Image: The Prologue & The Promise by [Bob McCall](http://www.mccallstudios.com/)*\",\"timestamp\":1638999714,\"title\":\"Stories of the Future: Bounties\"},\"digest\":\"lZMJaKcjA130AbzKL7HXgYRGcfK8IDSnmBFz4Oqub38\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd340d824F8A2BC6C7172b63B675B97E72eDD14F7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gj7ySeX7rmszPh-gTPF5npEzERg41_GfX0azwrbkAKY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RNcl3y_jAbl8M_MROsnHDVboPiaO9OkNGAXwkvNpegE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yTa10702mpYYVXKKWCaPda0UppiuzosonbpzgHebUqUJBYAX4EvKzmee1JhxR9PLmnfQdXz4xfSHHtn_15EVZw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x398359024ccb8ea57b7bc5f57970f7109d1150fdbca1de14d7843ebb346494902f4f810faf7d4ff2da524ef649b008004840fb3278729ade42a62fb705aea75c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gj7ySeX7rmszPh-gTPF5npEzERg41_GfX0azwrbkAKY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RNcl3y_jAbl8M_MROsnHDVboPiaO9OkNGAXwkvNpegE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ktGaU-jJKTfGWbvWxUZ5LyyHRQyDAJfxTude_U6AIKg\"}"